title: S.U.M.O Sessions - Live @ Hultsfred 14-06-2002-CHRIS_S [House]
description:
Not much to say - just that this is a really good house set recorded at the Hultsfred festival in Sweden, 2002. A lot of influences by latin and salsa, this warm house music makes you think of nothing but a hot summer outdoor party :)

Apart from Sp&aring;nka, swedish house musik doesn't get much better than this in my opinion. Download, seed and write a comment!

Party on // AssMaster
